        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/golden/mission_gecko/scene_gecko_basic.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 1e6d10fb-fdf7-4013-bf57-db2290b911b5).Image",
        "Description": "Every December, the Shiekh takes his staff on a winter get-away that culminates in the annual Holiday Snowball Fight. Fought between the staff that attends the household and the staff that attends the business, the event has resulted in more than a few deaths over the years. This year, however, has been derailed by the Sheikh&apos;s latest vanity project. The new faction leaders want to continue the tradition but lack snow. Perhaps each faction&apos;s signiature fruit will do? Who likes fruitcake anyways?",
